# Design generic Git platform adapter

Design abstraction layer for handling operations across different Git platforms.

## Requirements

- [ ] Design `PagServer.Integrations.Git.Adapter` behaviour
- [ ] Define standard operations:
  - [ ] PR creation/update
  - [ ] Issue creation/update
  - [ ] Comments
  - [ ] Repository information
  - [ ] Webhook management
- [ ] Document platform-specific implementations:
  - [ ] GitHub, Bitbucket, Gitea mappings
  - [ ] Authentication patterns
  - [ ] Rate limit handling
- [ ] Design platform detection strategy
- [ ] Document error handling patterns
- [ ] Create adapter pattern validation tests

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Behaviour module defined with standard operations
- [ ] Platform mappings clearly documented
- [ ] Operation interface supports all platforms
- [ ] Authentication patterns unified
- [ ] Example implementations for each platform
- [ ] Pattern tests verify adapter protocol
- [ ] `mix test` passes for all tests
- [ ] `mix lint` passes without warnings


